e="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">В потоке</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Nel diluvio</span></p><p begin="50.860" end="51.610" itunes:key="L7" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="50.860" end="51.100">In</span> <span begin="51.100" end="51.320">the</span> <span begin="51.320" end="51.610">fire</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">在那烈火之中</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">在那烈火之中</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">炎の中で</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">당신의 사랑</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Dans le feu</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">En el fuego</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Im Feuer</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">No fogo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">И в огне</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Nel fuoco</span></p><p begin="52.140" end="52.820" itunes:key="L8" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="52.140" end="52.330">Of</span> <span begin="52.330" end="52.490">your</span> <span begin="52.490" end="52.820">love</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">在您那慈爱的烈火之中</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">在您那慈愛的烈火之中</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">あなたの愛の</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">그 불꽃 속에서</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">De ton amour</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">De tu amor</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Deiner Liebe</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Do seu amor</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Твоей любви</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Del tuo amore</span></p><p begin="55.310" end="1:01.330" itunes:key="L9" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="55.310" end="56.000">Why</span> <span begin="56.000" end="56.460">ha</span><span begin="56.460" end="56.550">ve</span> <span begin="56.550" end="56.960">you</span> <span begin="56.960" end="57.120">f</span><span begin="57.120" end="57.500">or</span><span begin="57.500" end="57.780">s</span><span begin="57.780" end="59.670">a</span><span begin="59.670" end="59.970">ken</span> <span begin="59.970" end="1:01.330">us?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">为何您要将我们无情抛弃</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">為何您要將我們無情拋棄</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">何故我らを見捨てたのか</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">어찌하여 우리를 버리셨나이까?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Pourquoi nous as-tu abandonnées ?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">¿Por qué nos has abandonado?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Warum hast du uns verlassen?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Por que você nos abandonou?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Почему ты оставила нас</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Perché ci hai abbandonati</span></p><p begin="1:02.520" end="1:10.920" itunes:key="L10" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:02.520" end="1:03.120">Mo</span><span begin="1:03.120" end="1:03.700">ther</span> <span begin="1:03.700" end="1:04.310">of</span> <span begin="1:04.310" end="1:04.680">thi</span><span begin="1:04.680" end="1:04.930">s</span> <span begin="1:04.930" end="1:05.570">sa</span><span begin="1:05.570" end="1:05.920">cred</span> <span begin="1:06.160" end="1:06.600">dream</span> <span begin="1:06.750" end="1:07.100">that</span> <span begin="1:07.340" end="1:09.240">burn</span><span begin="1:09.240" end="1:09.340">s</span> <span begin="1:09.340" end="1:09.610">in</span> <span begin="1:09.610" end="1:10.920">us</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">致那孕育了 在我们心中熊熊燃烧的神圣之梦的慈母</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">致那孕育了 在我們心中熊熊燃燒的神聖之夢的慈母</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">我らの中で燃えるこの聖なる夢の母よ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">우리 안에서 타오르는 이 성스러운 꿈의 어머니시여</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Mère de ce rêve sacré qui brûle en nous</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Madre de este sueño sagrado que arde en nosotros</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Mutter dieses heiligen Traums der in uns brennt</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Mãe deste sonho sagrado que queima em nós</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Матерь этого священного сна что горит в нас</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Madre di questo sacro sogno che brucia in noi</span></p><p begin="1:12.140" end="1:21.100" itunes:key="L11" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:12.140" end="1:12.850">Will</span> <span begin="1:12.850" end="1:13.360">you</span> <span begin="1:13.360" end="1:13.990">hear</span> <span begin="1:13.990" end="1:14.540">our</span> <span begin="1:14.540" end="1:15.150">voi</span><span begin="1:15.150" end="1:15.750">ces</span> <span begin="1:15.750" end="1:16.270">ma</span><span begin="1:16.380" end="1:16.460">ke</span> <span begin="1:16.460" end="1:16.730">u</span><span begin="1:16.730" end="1:16.950">s</span> <span begin="1:16.950" end="1:18.970">glo</span><span begin="1:18.970" end="1:19.340">ri</span><span begin="1:19.340" end="1:21.100">ous?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">您能否听见我们的呼唤 赐予我们无上的荣耀</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">您能否聽見我們的呼喚 賜予我們無上的榮耀</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">我らの声を聞き栄光を与えてくれるのか</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">우리의 목소리를 들으시어 우릴 영광되게 하시렵니까?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Entendras-tu nos voix pour nous rendre glorieuses ?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">¿Escucharás nuestras voces hacernos gloriosos?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Wirst du unsere Stimmen hören uns glorreich machen?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Você ouvirá nossas vozes nos fará gloriosas?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Услышишь ли ты наши голоса одаришь ли нас величием</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Ascolterai le nostre voci rendici gloriosi</span></p><p begin="1:22.100" end="1:22.790" itunes:key="L12" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:22.100" end="1:22.340">Co</span><span begin="1:22.340" end="1:22.520">ver</span> <span begin="1:22.520" end="1:22.790">us</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">庇护我们吧</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">庇護我們吧</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">我らを包み込んで</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">우리를 감싸주소서</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Couvre-nous</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Cúbrenos</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Hülle uns ein</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Cubra-nos</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Укрой нас</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Avvolgici</span></p><p begin="1:23.320" end="1:23.950" itunes:key="L13" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:23.320" end="1:23.520">Ho</span><span begin="1:23.520" end="1:23.720">ly</span> <span begin="1:23.720" end="1:23.950">one</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">神圣的尊主</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">神聖的尊主</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">聖なる者よ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">거룩하신 이여</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Sainte</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Santa</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Heilige</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Sagrada</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">О Святая</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Santa</span></p><p begin="1:24.520" end="1:25.210" itunes:key="L14" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:24.520" end="1:24.680">In</span> <span begin="1:24.680" end="1:24.940">the</span> <span begin="1:24.94