630" end="1:58.650">us?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">为何您要将我们无情抛弃</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">為何您要將我們無情拋棄</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">何故我らを見捨てたのか</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">어찌하여 우리를 버리셨나이까?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Pourquoi nous as-tu abandonnées ?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">¿Por qué nos has abandonado?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Warum hast du uns verlassen?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Por que você nos abandonou?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Почему ты оставила нас</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Perché ci hai abbandonati</span></p><p begin="2:00.120" end="2:08.320" itunes:key="L17" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:00.120" end="2:00.630">Mo</span><span begin="2:00.760" end="2:01.400">ther</span> <span begin="2:01.400" end="2:01.800">o</span><span begin="2:01.800" end="2:01.870">f</span> <span begin="2:02.020" end="2:02.340">thi</span><span begin="2:02.340" end="2:02.520">s</span> <span begin="2:02.520" end="2:02.970">cur</span><span begin="2:03.120" end="2:03.620">sed</span> <span begin="2:03.770" end="2:04.280">ra</span><span begin="2:04.280" end="2:04.470">ge</span> <span begin="2:04.470" end="2:04.810">that</span> <span begin="2:05.050" end="2:06.840">burn</span><span begin="2:06.840" end="2:06.950">s</span> <span begin="2:06.950" end="2:07.170">in</span> <span begin="2:07.170" end="2:08.320">us</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">致那孕育了 在我们心中熊熊燃烧的受诅狂怒的慈母</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">致那孕育了 在我們心中熊熊燃燒的受詛狂怒的慈母</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">我らの中で燃えるこの呪われた怒りの母よ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">우리 안에서 타오르는 이 저주받은 분노의 어머니시여</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Mère de cette rage maudite qui brûle en nous</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" x